Results

For each of the experiment scenario we show the Yellow robot's estimation of the physical and social goal of the red robot at each time step.

Using S-MDP, at different levels of reasoning, Yellow robot estimates the physical and social goal of the red robot at each time step. The lines in blue is our Social MDP scores, green in green is Inverse planning, purple in purple is the cue-based model, and in dotted is the ground truth.

Experiment Result for Scenario 1

Red robot is initialized with the physical goal of Flower and social goal of -2. Yellow robot is initialized with the physical goal of Tree and social goal of -2. Using S-MDP at different levels of reasoning, Yellow robot estimates the physical and social goal of the red robot at each time step.
